description: `Start Interview` button opens the interview page
`Show Current Tags (intermediate result)` button that shows the tags
`Home` button returns to the home page and restarts the interview and data
`Download Transcript` button that downloads the transcript
`Revisit this question` button that revisits a specific question
`Write Feedback` button that opens the feedback input
`Write Personal Comment` button that opens the comment input
`Show Conclusion` button that opens the conclusion page
`Home` button that returns to the home page and restarts the interview and data
`Download Conclusions` button that downloads the conclusions
`Submit Feedback` button that submits the feedback
`Submit Personal Comment` button that submits the comment
`Show Transcript` button that shows the transcript of the interview
